1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,500
I found a 1994 polaroid

2
00:00:02,500 --> 00:00:04,800
that breaks reality.

3
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:07,500
They were at a restaurant.

4
00:00:07,500 --> 00:00:09,800
I was flipping through

5
00:00:09,800 --> 00:00:12,000
the wedding album,

6
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:15,500
the background caught my eye.

7
00:00:15,500 --> 00:00:19,000
A man stands behind them.

8
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:23,000
He wears modern wireless earbuds.

9
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:27,000
They didn't exist thirty years ago.

10
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:29,500
I checked the print

11
00:00:29,500 --> 00:00:32,500
with a magnifying loupe.

12
00:00:32,500 --> 00:00:35,500
His face is blurred,

13
00:00:35,500 --> 00:00:39,000
like a corrupted digital file.

14
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:41,000
How does a print

15
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:43,000
have a digital glitch?